item.title: Handmade Paper Goods
item.description: I like to doodle. And I like to create one-of-a-kind cards and paper goods that convey a warmth not possible from manufactured items. Let’s discuss how I can help convey your messages to friends with that extra personal touch.

item.title: Floral Decor
item.description: Flowers make the occasion special. I can help you do it economically, so that you can truly enjoy hosting your event.

item.title: Charcuterie
item.description: I love creating beautiful boards and trays filled with cheeses, cold cuts, crackers, nuts, fruit and garnishes. Let’s discuss what can be created for your event. Your guests will love it!

item.title: Event Decor
item.description: Describe what I’ve created as decorations for special events.
